<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.238.116168.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. The partitioned Maximum Likelihood (ML) phylogenetic tree inferred from the genomic SNP dataset using IQ-TREE, showing the four subclades within Perilimnastes [Phyllagathis (raphide) clade]. For the nodes without full support, values from SH-aLRT test (left) and ultrafast bootstrap (right) are given at the nodes. The new species is indicated with a star. Lineages with raphides are noted with solid circles." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/977223" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

